body_html: Yes it is. I am still waiting for new opinions. I guess while_loop could not be compiled or optimised in general situations. I also tried implementing DBSCAN using tf. Same algorithm with tf is just a bit better than using numpy, but much worse than the built in implementation in scikit, with cython. It is disappointing to see my friend's matlab implementation is faster than mine.
